```mermaid
erDiagram
PRODUCT {
  Int PK Product_ID
    String Product_Name
    Boolean Product_Price
}
CUSTOMER {
  Int PK Costomer_ID
    String Costomer_Name
}
SALE {
  Int Sale ID
    Int FK Costomer_ID
    Int FK Product_ID
}
INVENTORY {
  Int Inventory ID
    Int FK Product_ID
    Int Quantity
}
```
